data.description: Assumable VA loan @2.25%! Stunning Palm Shores home - 4/2 split floor plan home. Home exudes pride in ownership and holds a desirable single story open concept, split floor plan. The grand primary space includes 10ft ceilings and tiled flooring throughout. A spacious living room connects to the dining area/breakfast nook and gourmet custom kitchen with maple cabinets and granite countertops. The master is an owner's haven, complete with double walk-in closets, and a private ensuite with double sink vanity and a large tiled surround shower. All of the bedrooms hold hardwood floors and plenty of storage, as well as square footage. Private fenced lot ready for you to enjoy. Minutes to beach/river access and close to Patrick SFB!
